---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Adam Drew">
  <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text-primary dark:text-text-dark-primary mb-8">Adam Drew</h1>

  <section class="max-w-2xl">
    <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary dark:text-text-dark-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4">I'm a Developer at Red Hat, where I work on cloud-native technologies and developer tools. My focus is on building software that helps developers be more productive and effective in their work.</p>

    <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary dark:text-text-dark-secondary leading-relaxed">I'm passionate about open source, DevOps practices, and creating elegant solutions to complex problems. When I'm not coding, you'll find me exploring new technologies, contributing to open source projects, or writing about what I've learned.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
